{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"15e9726e-d168-4e14-9a03-fb6c69161fce","content":"**Yes, you will hit a compatibility issue.** MSTest v4 (the `4.x` line) dropped support for .NET 6.0. It requires **net8.0 or later**.\n\nYour options:\n\n1. **Upgrade your target framework** to `net8.0` (or `net9.0`), then move to MSTest v4.\n2. **Stay on MSTest v3** (`3.8.x`) if you need to keep targeting `net6.0`.\n\nNote that .NET 6.0 itself has been out of support since November 2024, so upgrading the TFM is generally recommended.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"dd193803-5aaf-493d-9db6-2299f3c6333d","outputTokens":150},"id":"717eeb29-8b89-4956-a72d-6558ce2f75a3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:22:44.556Z","parentId":"cd7e7abd-f1c3-44cb-a650-596f2fbcc819"}
